_sText:
Welcome to Breakfloor Redefined!!

First of all, I know everyone is going to say, this is just a copy of Breakfloor with new textures.  In a sense, yes it is, but I never copy pieces from the original .vmf's of the maps I remake.

Everything in this map has been made from scratch using the old .vmf as a stencil/skeleton to work from.  

Changes:
-Optimization changes throughout the entire build/map.
-Lighting/texture changes from the original
-Minor aesthetic changes (my own personal wants)
-Other minor tweaks that I need not be specific about.

All in all, its Breakfloor, what more could you want if your a fanatic?  I tried to stay true to the original map without ruining what everyone found amusing/fun from the older version.

Comments and ratings are always appreciated!!

Any problems/bugs/complaints/suggestions can all be directed to:

Xfire: Wowyourgaiy
Email: Phantomoper3@comcast.net


Thanks and I hope you all enjoy.
